```
# Julia installation and related files
julia-*/
**/julia-*/

# Julia compiled files and caches
**/*.ji
**/*.so
**/base.cache
**/compiled/

# Compressed files
*.gz
*.tar
*.tgz
*.bz2
*.xz
*.zst
*.lz4
*.lzh
*.cab
*.arj
*.rpm
*.deb
*.Z
*.lz
*.lzo
*.tar.gz
